import React from 'react';

export const homeObjOne = {
    lightBg: false,
    lightText: true,
    lightTextDesc: true,
    topLine: 'Take your Business to the next level',
    headline: 'Take your Business to the next level',
    description:
      'We help you fulfill your best potential through our skills on Web Development and UI Design',
    buttonLabel: 'Get Started',
    imgStart: '',
    img: 'images/svg_header.svg',
    alt: 'Credit Card'
  };

  export const homeObjTwo = {
    lightBg: true,
    lightText: false,
    lightTextDesc: false,
    topLine: 'We love React',
    headline: 'Web Development',
    description:
      "It’s all about the coding and programming that powers the website’s functionality. It can be broken down into frontend (React) and backend (Node).",
    buttonLabel: 'Start Now',
    imgStart: 'start',
    img: 'images/svg_web_development.svg',
    alt: 'Vault'
  };  

  export const homeObjThree = {
    lightBg: true,
    lightText: false,
    lightTextDesc: false,
    topLine: 'We use Adobe Xd',
    headline: 'UI Design',
    description:
      'The User Interface Design is the graphical layout of an application or website. This includes screen layout, transitions, interface  and every single micro-interaction. ',
    buttonLabel: 'Learn More',
    imgStart: '',
    img: 'images/svg_ui_design.svg',
    alt: 'Vault'
  };

  export const homeObjFour = {
    lightBg: false,
    lightText: true,
    lightTextDesc: true,
    topLine: 'WEB DESIGN',
    headline: 'CMS',
    description:
      'Whether you’re looking for a custom content management system (CMS) platform as WordPress, our experienced team can deliver exactly what you need.',
    buttonLabel: 'Sign Up Now',
    imgStart: 'start',
    img: 'images/svg__web_design_cms.svg',
    alt: 'Vault'
  };

  export const homeObjFive = {
    lightBg: false,
    lightText: true,
    lightTextDesc: true,
    topLine: 'You Deserve a Host You Can Depend on',
    headline: 'Hosting',
    description:
      "There are two things you need for visitors to be able to access your website: a hosting service and a domain name, and we can provide both.",
    buttonLabel: 'Start Now',
    imgStart: '',
    img: 'images/svg_ui_design.svg',
    alt: 'Vault'
  };
